1
00:00:05,420 --> 00:00:06,670
Mizuki.

2
00:00:08,430 --> 00:00:11,090
What are you doing here?

3
00:00:11,890 --> 00:00:12,890
Mizuki.

4
00:00:13,560 --> 00:00:14,600
I'm so sorry!

5
00:00:14,600 --> 00:00:16,770
It's all my fault.

6
00:00:16,770 --> 00:00:20,190
You don't need to apologize.
It makes me feel like a child.

7
00:00:20,190 --> 00:00:21,690
That's not true.

8
00:00:22,560 --> 00:00:24,440
I'm the one acting like a child.

9
00:00:26,530 --> 00:00:30,990
Without you, Mizuki,
I wouldn't even have food to eat.

10
00:00:31,240 --> 00:00:33,370
Or be able to wake up in the morning.

11
00:00:33,370 --> 00:00:38,410
I might have started working first,

12
00:00:38,410 --> 00:00:40,000
but I'm still so immature.

13
00:00:41,290 --> 00:00:44,210
I always panic
over the smallest things.

14
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:52,550
I've just been taking advantage
of your kindness.

15
00:00:52,550 --> 00:00:56,600
I wanted to make things easier for you
and stand on my own two feet.

16
00:00:58,350 --> 00:01:02,350
But the harder I tried,
the more I messed up.

17
00:01:04,230 --> 00:01:06,650
That's why...

18
00:01:08,150 --> 00:01:10,820
That's why...

19
00:01:15,370 --> 00:01:20,710
Silly, you're crying like a baby.

20
00:01:23,830 --> 00:01:26,340
I'm sorry.

21
00:01:26,340 --> 00:01:29,760
I'm sorry, too.

22
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:33,130
I was meddling too much.

23
00:01:33,130 --> 00:01:38,520
I should have trusted you more.

24
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:43,850
Hinata.
